data.description: Centrally located and plenty of yard space make this charming home the right one for you. With a pull around drive and easy enter exit from the one car garage you can take your time to show off the garden and shady trees to all your neighbors. With plenty of unique features such as custom kitchen and built in fish tank at the bar and the large back yard, this house has everything someone would need and tons of Charm!
